Returns an empty table

Source: R/visTable.R
emptyTable.Rd

Returns an empty table

Usage

emptyTable(type = "gt")

Arguments

type

The desired format of the output table. See tableType() for allowed options.

Value

An empty table of the class specified in type

Examples

emptyTable(type = "flextable")

Table has no data
